    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a transformation and represents an incredible opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to return to its best self, it's a fantastic foundation for a dedicated restoration. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
